             was indicted for <rs id="t18010916-32-off155" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18010916-32-off155" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010916-32-off155" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18010916-32-cd156" type="crimeDate">15th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010916-32-off155 t18010916-32-cd156"></join>, seventeen pounds weight of indigo, value 4l.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18010916-32-victim227" type="victimName">
                  Thomas-Downes 
                  Lamb
               <interp inst="t18010916-32-victim227" type="surname" value="Lamb"></interp>
